Subject: [PATCH 5/6] Documentation/ABI: mark /sys/kernel/fadump_* sysfs files
 deprecated

References: bsc#1160018 ltc#182902 jsc#SLE-9099
Patch-mainline: submitted https://patchwork.ozlabs.org/cover/1207835/

Add a deprecation note in FADump sysfs ABI documentation files and move
them from ABI/testing to ABI/obsolete directory.

Signed-off-by: Sourabh Jain <sourabhjain@linux.ibm.com>
Acked-by: Michal Suchanek <msuchanek@suse.de>
